07:44.579 --> 07:45.881
Oh, that is here.

07:46.148 --> 07:48.551
The new fragrance for men
by Gio.

07:51.852 --> 07:53.687
Natalie, look, I'm so sorry.

07:53.689 --> 07:55.754
- <i>Jared.</i>
- Look, this whole time apart...

