09:12.434 --> 09:14.134
No, no, no, no.

09:14.136 --> 09:16.805
Saying anything
but programmed responses.

09:18.973 --> 09:20.075
No, no, no.

09:21.108 --> 09:22.110
No, no.

09:23.111 --> 09:24.713
Stop following me.

09:24.979 --> 09:26.348
Stop it.

09:31.319 --> 09:34.155
<i>You aren't thinking
of killing yourself anymore.</i>

09:37.324 --> 09:39.926
<i>When faced with the mysteries
of the universe,</i>

09:39.928 --> 09:41.897
<i>life once again
seems appealing.</i>

09:43.397 --> 09:44.733
What do you want?

09:45.834 --> 09:46.801
<i>I want to show you
my Berlin.</i>

