show you my Berlin!

15:33.680 --> 15:34.714
Okay.

15:34.716 --> 15:36.418
- <i>Adorable...</i>
- Coming.

15:36.617 --> 15:39.487
<i>...avoid-at-all-costs Rose.</i>

16:00.775 --> 16:02.211
Go away.

16:04.145 --> 16:05.477
