16:15.522 --> 16:16.624
Then give me whiskey.

16:17.391 --> 16:18.593
Out too.

16:19.795 --> 16:21.094
Come on, Michail.
Stop playing games with me here.

16:21.096 --> 16:22.398
Sorry. Can't do it.

16:23.464 --> 16:25.630
Didn't you say I reminded you
of your older brother?

16:25.632 --> 16:27.069
Is this how you treat a brother?

16:27.267 --> 16:28.768
No wonder he died.

16:28.770 --> 16:31.537
He didn't die.
We saved his life.

16:31.539 --> 16:33.074
Me and the whole family.

16:33.507 --> 16:34.773
No money anymore for drinks.

16:34.775 --> 16:36.408
He was crying like little baby,

16:36.410 --> 16:38.414
trying to carve himself
with his knife.

16:39.314 --> 16:41.114
Now, he's working
for Google.

16:41.116 --> 16:44.116
Michail, I really had
a bad day, okay?

16:44.118 --> 16:45.521
You sound exactly like him.

16:45.886 --> 16:47.256
I'll pay for it.

16:49.723 --> 16:50.658
Are you sure?

16:51.391 --> 16:52.658
He's not an angel.

16:52.660 --> 16:53.793
It's just costume.

16:53.795 --> 16:55.564
You heard her. The lady pays.

16:59.133 --> 17:00.398
Good-karma girl, huh?

17:00.400 --> 17:01.402
So?

17:01.835 --> 17:03.504
It's 11.99.

17:08.541 --> 17:10.145
You're making me feel
really bad here.

17:10.912 --> 17:13.482
Actually, worse than our
Russian dissident just did.

17:14.281 --> 17:16.385
Hey, I'm just inviting
an angel for a drink.

17:17.519 --> 17:18.685
You're right, Michail,

17:19.354 --> 17:20.720
the last thing to go

17:20.722 --> 17:22.089
is really a man's pride.

17:35.403 --> 17:37.470
His mom's gonna
be back in a few days.

17:37.472 --> 17:40.173
She might not be. His brother
is still in the hospital.

17:40.175 --> 17:42.775
Yeah. But, moving him now,
it's gonna devastate him.

17:42.777 --> 17:44.844
This is another new place
with more new people.

17:44.846 --> 17:46.711
I think he's never
going to see them again.

17:46.713 --> 17:48.748
Look, it's not ideal.
I'm not arguing that.

17:48.750 --> 17:50.586
But they're not gonna
let him stay here.

18:17.311 --> 18:18.678
Excuse me?

18:18.680 --> 18:19.744
Yeah?

18:19.746 --> 18:20.779
Um, chicken.

18:20.781 --> 18:21.782
Chicken? Yes.

18:28.423 --> 18:30.659
Liv, um, Nisar Raslan,

18:30.892 --> 18:33.226
is there any way we can make
an exception for him?

18:33.228 --> 18:34.492
- Who?
- The, uh, little boy

18:34.494 --> 18:36.494
who's younger brother
is in the hospital.

18:36.496 --> 18:38.230
- Oh, yeah.
- Yeah.

18:38.232 --> 18:40.365
Could we possibly let him
stay here one more night?

18:40.367 --> 18:43.405
I wish we could
but absolutely not.

18:43.905 --> 18:47.940
We can call the Jugendamt
ask not to try and place him

18:47.942 --> 18:50.875
until we know when the mother
will be returning.

18:50.877 --> 18:53.514
But he can't stay here
unchaperoned.

21:01.108 --> 21:03.008
- Oh, hello, darling.
- Hello.

21:03.010 --> 21:05.377
I can't believe
you don't have olive oil here.

21:05.379 --> 21:07.413
I mean, how can you cook
without olive oil,

21:07.415 --> 21:08.517
the base of all...

21:09.916 --> 21:10.985
what's this?

21:11.685 --> 21:12.920
This is Nisar.

21:15.155 --> 21:16.390
Hello.

21:19.126 --> 21:20.796
Do you wanna sit down?

21:22.896 --> 21:25.530
Oh, do you want
something to drink?

21:25.532 --> 21:27.601
Like, uh...
I only got water.

21:27.801 --> 21:29.704
Water? No?

21:30.037 --> 21:31.006
Okay.

21:32.740 --> 21:34.675
So, is he from the shelter?

21:36.644 --> 21:38.914
I know what I think
you might like.

21:40.080 --> 21:42.818
Well... is he?

21:43.151 --> 21:45.087
No. I picked him up
in an alleyway.

21:46.820 --> 21:47.822
Here, look.

21:55.195 --> 21:56.694
Could you just stop
with the Arabic

21:56.696 --> 21:58.099
long enough to tell me
what's going on?

21:59.200 --> 22:00.365
Well, he only
understands Arabic.

22:00.367 --> 22:02.971
It's the only thing he has
in his life he hasn't lost.

22:04.739 --> 22:06.441
And is he staying here?

22:07.742 --> 22:09.944
Should we go
outside for a second?

22:11.846 --> 22:13.415
Two seconds, okay?

22:19.453 --> 22:20.553
Look, he's just here
for the night.

22:20.555 --> 22:22.855
His little brother is in
the hospital with pneumonia.

22:22.857 --> 22:23.990
And his mom is staying with him.

22:23.992 --> 22:26.759
I can't leave him in the shelter
alone. It's not allowed.

22:26.761 --> 22:28.029
Well, what about his father?

22:28.628 --> 22:30.128
Well, his father
didn't come with them.

22:30.130 --> 22:32.131
And they were going to
give him to child services.

22:32.133 --> 22:34.232
If he goes to child services,
I don't know how long

22:34.234 --> 22:36.067
it will be before I can
get him back to his mom.

22:36.069 --> 22:37.068
So, he's staying the night here?

22:37.070 --> 22:39.974
Yes. It's just one night.
That's what it is.

22:40.875 --> 22:43.642
Oh, when you're in the
hospital with pneumonia

22:43.644 --> 22:46.013
you were there for two weeks,
remember? What then?

22:46.746 --> 22:48.482
We didn't catch it
in time.

22:48.883 --> 22:50.184
He isn't going to live
that long.

22:51.018 --> 22:52.854
Oh, God.

22:54.489 --> 22:55.557
Oh.

22:56.523 --> 22:58.190
Oh, God. Jane, what are you
putting yourself

22:58.192 --> 22:59.493
into the middle of?

23:00.595 --> 23:02.731
<i>Oh, boy. Oh, boy.</i>

23:04.499 --> 23:05.800
<i>Woo-hoo.</i>

23:16.511 --> 23:18.743
I mean, are you even
allowed to bring him here?

23:18.745 --> 23:21.145
You... maybe you could lose
your job for this.

23:21.147 --> 23:23.147
Mom, can you please
remember that he's watching?

23:23.149 --> 23:25.183
Well, I thought you said
he only understands Arabic?

23:25.185 --> 23:26.818
No.
He can understand tone.

23:26.820 --> 23:28.721
He can understand everything.

23:28.723 --> 23:31.693
Jane, just think
what you're taking on here.

23:37.697 --> 23:39.967
All right. All right.
I'm done. I'm done.

23:41.068 --> 23:42.835
It'd be nice
to have another guest.

23:42.837 --> 23:44.873
Look. I cooked for you.

23:47.073 --> 23:49.074
Lemon roast chicken.
You're favorite.

23:49.076 --> 23:50.808
You cooked?
Why did you cook?

23:50.810 --> 23:53.178
